title: Baby yogurt
review: We brought the Stonyfield yogurt pouch for grandkids, so they can have something else besides the baby food. Give them a treat. For the most part they seem to enjoy it. It's organic and has milk, so it's good.They both will eat it. Price is reasonable.

name: Willie V. Hughes
title: My Toddler Son's Favorite
review: Great yogurt for on the go families with kids who want a snack. Low mess, healthy, tastes great, and my son can control the flow. I need to help him get the last small bit out by rolling it up from the bottom, but I don't mind.
